steps.name: I am on the VA Login page
I have entered a valid username and password of VA login page
I am on the Azure Video Indexer Main page
The page displays a search box where a search GovTechRewind query can be entered
Clicking Search will perform the search GovTechRewind query and display relevant search results
The search query bar allows the filtering of search results by Scope of search
The search query bar allows the filtering of search results by Insight Type
a search is performed, the page will display a listing of 3 GovTechRewind videos that have been indexed
Hovering the cursor over each video tile will reveal video information
User can toggle between a list view
User can toggle between a tiled view

name: Search video indexer service
description: As a User, I can search for videos containing any text, person, insights or object specified within the indexed videos visible to me.
